sources.title: Bitches, The, Les Chiennes 1973
sources.description: Janine Reynaud's character Viriane hires Eric to service her and her close friends. Eric is played by director Michel Lemoine who also had a hand in writing the film. I guess he could not find anyone else capable of bringing his creation to life. I am sure it is just coincidental that he ends up naked with half a dozen gorgeous women.Â  French with English Subtitles
